  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bae\u0bc2\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "One of the three who walked around with swords was caught",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "In Jaffna's Vattukkottai, theft, robbery and banditry are on the rise, and a man was caught by the youth of the village while threatening people with swords.",
        "When one of the Vattukkottai youths observed it and tried to cross the road with suspicion, the motorcycle they were traveling in met with an accident and fell on the road. Two of them managed to drop their swords and escaped while one was trapped with injuries.",
        "A Moolai resident who was caught with the swords was handed over to the Vattukkottai police. The police also seized two swords and mortars. (a)"
      ],
